       'WATER_LACK_VL', 'SPL_TPRT_1', 'HTNG_TPRT_1', 'SPL_TPRT_2',

for i in range(1, len(fruit_setting)):

    plt.scatter(df_result['STRG_DT'], df_result[fruit_setting[i]], s=point_size)
    plt.title(fruit_setting[i])
    plt.grid(True)
